Additional Acknowledgments:

This project is developed for the AWS AI for Bharat Hackathon 2026 and uses
various AWS services including Amazon Bedrock, Amazon Bedrock Knowledge Bases,
and other AWS technologies.

The agricultural knowledge and data used in this system are sourced from:
- Indian Council of Agricultural Research (ICAR)
- India Meteorological Department (IMD)
- National Agricultural Market (eNAM)
- Various state agricultural departments and research institutions

This software is intended to support Indian farmers and promote sustainable
agricultural practices in alignment with UN Sustainable Development Goals.
